Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.91,0:00:25.39,Main,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Macross Galaxy:
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.00,0:00:27.00,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\c&HE9B69D&\pos(360,176)}Je to vlekoucí se sbohem.
